description:
JetBrains ReSharper Code Annotations.

      ReSharper annotations are useful to increase accuracy and precision of ReSharper code
      inspections results, reduce false positive warnings? explicitly declare nullability
      of values in your code, deal with implicit usages of members, support special semantics
      of ASP.NET and XAML frameworks APIs.

      Annotations are erased from metadata by default, so no actual binary reference
      to 'JetBrains.Annotations.dll' assembly will be produced. If you need to preserve
      annotations in metadata, just define 'JETBRAINS_ANNOTATIONS' conditional compilation
      symbol in your projects.
title: JetBrains ReSharper Annotations
